{"tid":712554,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇過老子道德經","createTime":"2018-06-22T07:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T11:27:44.000Z","uid":74390,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0a1c723434ebbe3fa56a5152a017609454a98e","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"道德經<br />\n<br />\n第一章<br />\n<br />\n「道可道，非常道，名可名，非常名。無名，天地之始，有名，萬物之母。故常無欲以觀其妙，常有欲以觀其徼，此兩者同出而異名，同謂之玄，玄之又玄，眾妙之門。」"},{"pid":"401e6ef96cbc0c2312de71ca7b38cd6d88f4f6a0","tid":712554,"uid":147459,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"冇，d連登仔認為中文係垃圾而英文係寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb10797a56bed160e706e5dec13c5e56d76243a","tid":712554,"uid":2032,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"道德經其實真係好撚屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應用喺現今社會好啱"},{"pid":"f2da929beb62d43138d5a55eb0b492c481e170cf","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"5e0a1c723434ebbe3fa56a5152a017609454a98e","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"道德經<br />\n<br />\n第一章<br />\n<br />\n「道可道，非常道，名可名，非常名。無名，天地之始，有名，萬物之母。故常無欲以觀其妙，常有欲以觀其徼，此兩者同出而異名，同謂之玄，玄之又玄，眾妙之門。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"「道」一樣野，暫時當係道理既意思，因老子為道家既宗師，睇成所有人，事物，原理，運行，既野都稱為道。<br />\n「可道」呢個道應該是動詞，第一個是名詞，「可道」即係「道」可以運行，運作。<br />\n「非常道」唔係平常所知既道，唔係平常所知的方法。"},{"pid":"d692a2074591b7dc49232901f98f7f40b33fca17","tid":712554,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"edb10797a56bed160e706e5dec13c5e56d76243a","tid":712554,"uid":2032,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"道德經其實真係好撚屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應用喺現今社會好啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"道德經大部分觀念都同西方依家好流行既Stoicism 好相近。 有效推廣其實對近代人思想有好大益處"},{"pid":"8a8f881b3d94807a4a09f304beaafa5ea7be7135","tid":712554,"uid":50060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:40:58.000Z","msg":"老莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8a5c83b00bbc21bcb045d1918156ba052f7851","tid":712554,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:43:05.000Z","msg":"睇過<br />\n幾乎咩都唔記得<br />\n淨係記得有d唔太適用現代社會"},{"pid":"1217294607e7e2fc3fa49ef8e5abf0b6af4e5353","tid":712554,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"你搵本註釋睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058131596f3311a61fdab122066d964bca6c7fbe","tid":712554,"uid":147459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"LM，想學野"},{"pid":"0959be8189ff52921fc1f871f418167d0b762b8c","tid":712554,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名字"},{"pid":"2a830dfaaa2759e4df2f4b341ec66b52eda8f492","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:46:00.000Z","msg":"「名」呢個名，是一種野，通常剛剛開始或誕生或初期，要改名。<br />\n「可名」可以叫乜名都得，只係老子叫呢樣叫「道」。<br />\n「非常名」，呢度又「非常名」即係改個名比佢，唔係只係比個名佢咁簡單。<br />\n應該有仲深層次既意思係度？"},{"pid":"5cdf1da458e55b08fc0188848373ae0e699556cd","tid":712554,"uid":164387,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:48:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c229eea3d0e50773a9d4c694b044789565bed7ae","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1217294607e7e2fc3fa49ef8e5abf0b6af4e5353","tid":712554,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"你搵本註釋睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"其實一百個人睇完，可能有一百種睇法，個個睇法唔同，但又好似講得通"},{"pid":"d2b7d237c24c9d22b4166b67aed3c4016292dd75","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"「無名，天地之始」<br />\n<br />\n天地之始，係混沌？定係乜都未有既時候既境界？<br />\n即係點叫佢都未知既時侯，就係無名。<br />\n定係未知會點既時候都叫無名？"},{"pid":"82a8897fdafe5cb4c3009a4fcd6b8b65186867eb","tid":712554,"uid":98431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c229eea3d0e50773a9d4c694b044789565bed7ae","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1217294607e7e2fc3fa49ef8e5abf0b6af4e5353","tid":712554,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"你搵本註釋睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"其實一百個人睇完，可能有一百種睇法，個個睇法唔同，但又好似講得通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"無錯 但係睇你上面 好似連最基本斷句同意思都解錯<br />\n<br />\n道可道 指可以被指明 點出既「道」 <br />\n<br />\n非常道 指並非真正的「道」<br />\n<br />\n至於咩係「道」 老子假設佢存在 <br />\n<br />\n但係並唔能夠用形而下既任何事物/文字指稱 但卻又無處不在<br />\n<br />\n利申 淨係大學聽過幾堂書"},{"pid":"3d5388eee806fed49df38c837d4fda30ed589743","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:57:56.000Z","msg":"有名，萬物之母<br />\n<br />\n萬物之母，萬物發展出現了一樣，係呢一樣野令所有野得以發展，佢係「有名」？<br />\n定係後尾諗返轉頭，因為呢樣野令所有野得以發展，所以先比返個名比佢？"},{"pid":"a5040f4b612908de8963ea83465e8cc5f05b661f","tid":712554,"uid":130616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d692a2074591b7dc49232901f98f7f40b33fca17","tid":712554,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"edb10797a56bed160e706e5dec13c5e56d76243a","tid":712554,"uid":2032,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"道德經其實真係好撚屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應用喺現今社會好啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"道德經大部分觀念都同西方依家好流行既Stoicism 好相近。 有效推廣其實對近代人思想有好大益處"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:06:19.000Z","msg":"大佬，你噏乜鳩呀"},{"pid":"d6251c32ca7194fcfc3f00486def8855faa83763","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"故常無欲以觀其妙，常有欲以觀其徼<br />\n<br />\n徼：音嬌，外形，邊界既意思。<br />\n<br />\n觀其妙，妙就係心領神會，要無欲先可以領略到。<br />\n觀其徼，睇外表，用眼係睇，要有欲先可以睇到。<br />\n<br />\n呢度又對應上面「無名，天地之始，有名，萬物之母。」<br />\n<br />\n即係又有一種對比係度？"},{"pid":"885a08d2f755ed692f3908654255707d102d2f30","tid":712554,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"四書五經讀左無壞"},{"pid":"3b4fb60d706c8cea71a189d8ad75d7c4129bbc04","tid":712554,"uid":51509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"Dao is dao, very dao<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345f986e070256a3df120b9a4a7b7b1fa25661a4","tid":712554,"uid":147459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"885a08d2f755ed692f3908654255707d102d2f30","tid":712554,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"四書五經讀左無壞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:11:26.000Z","msg":"係，可惜香港豬只係重視所謂ge國際語言而仇視中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5071390aa3e6cde82e3a6e89981448f170801061","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"此兩者同出而異名，同謂之玄<br />\n<br />\n呢次大獲啦，此兩者係邊兩者？<br />\nA「道」「名」<br />\nB「無名」「有名」<br />\nC「無欲」「有欲」<br />\nD 以上皆是<br />\nE 以上皆不是<br />\n<br />\n同出而異名<br />\n<br />\n同出而兩種命名？不同叫法？不同意思？<br />\n<br />\n同謂之玄，又一樣叫「玄」"},{"pid":"a143060ab9fd5c0c38e42c7485bf9a860e83dc2f","tid":712554,"uid":29381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:15:00.000Z","msg":"睇你解釋得啖笑"},{"pid":"d4178303d30361aff29d00ace30be7ea6fda041c","tid":712554,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"82a8897fdafe5cb4c3009a4fcd6b8b65186867eb","tid":712554,"uid":98431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c229eea3d0e50773a9d4c694b044789565bed7ae","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1217294607e7e2fc3fa49ef8e5abf0b6af4e5353","tid":712554,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"你搵本註釋睇下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"其實一百個人睇完，可能有一百種睇法，個個睇法唔同，但又好似講得通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"無錯 但係睇你上面 好似連最基本斷句同意思都解錯<br />\n<br />\n道可道 指可以被指明 點出既「道」 <br />\n<br />\n非常道 指並非真正的「道」<br />\n<br />\n至於咩係「道」 老子假設佢存在 <br />\n<br />\n但係並唔能夠用形而下既任何事物/文字指稱 但卻又無處不在<br />\n<br />\n利申 淨係大學聽過幾堂書"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"唔識就唔好衝出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15564b982f179909222a204de7549a3c2851998e","tid":712554,"uid":79362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"從道德經悟出股票必勝之道<br />\n詳見世紀之戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98c91e60e24adc38520d54f10a4bc826c55139d","tid":712554,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4178303d30361aff29d00ace30be7ea6fda041c","tid":712554,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"82a8897fdafe5cb4c3009a4fcd6b8b65186867eb","tid":712554,"uid":98431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"c229eea3d0e50773a9d4c694b044789565bed7ae","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"其實一百個人睇完，可能有一百種睇法，個個睇法唔同，但又好似講得通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"無錯 但係睇你上面 好似連最基本斷句同意思都解錯<br />\n<br />\n道可道 指可以被指明 點出既「道」 <br />\n<br />\n非常道 指並非真正的「道」<br />\n<br />\n至於咩係「道」 老子假設佢存在 <br />\n<br />\n但係並唔能夠用形而下既任何事物/文字指稱 但卻又無處不在<br />\n<br />\n利申 淨係大學聽過幾堂書"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"唔識就唔好衝出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:17:25.000Z","msg":"咁你指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822269c580da2c36bfff4e19d22eacfb378a030d","tid":712554,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"我有個世界紀錄，乜鳩萬人齊頌道德經<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614f93673990778340c58db2953fdd86c86de408","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:20:43.000Z","msg":"玄之又玄，眾妙之門<br />\n<br />\n玄左N次之後，又玄<br />\n「玄」唔明既野，搞到明白之後，又唔明過，又再明，無限loop<br />\n<br />\n眾妙之門<br />\n<br />\n妙，前文有提出，無欲以觀其「妙」。要「無欲」才可領略。<br />\n呢度講「眾」，即係唔止一個，係好多個。<br />\n門，好明顯話，你明晒前面所講既野，你就知道門係邊度。或者知道個方法係乜野。"},{"pid":"4605615114991b93436d54cd9575adda6452d8e7","tid":712554,"uid":74390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a143060ab9fd5c0c38e42c7485bf9a860e83dc2f","tid":712554,"uid":29381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:15:00.000Z","msg":"睇你解釋得啖笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T08:21:40.000Z","msg":"多謝，我都係搏大家一笑"},{"pid":"9ced9b483e0403ba88060c984c207510996f8665","tid":712554,"uid":31827,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f98c91e60e24adc38520d54f10a4bc826c55139d","tid":712554,"uid":98431,"